data.message: Why isn't my newsfeed loading properly? it stops & says if I want more to add friends? I already have over 100 friends & am a member of many groups. Why has this just started in the last hour? I wasn't having any issues this morning.

replies.message: Hi Parisa. Your News Feed should be filled with updates from your friends and people and Pages you follow. If your News Feed is blank, try refreshing your page. If it's still missing stories, let us know at: http://bit.ly/2tDkan3. -Jessica

It is only when I click on Most recent feed. It stops after a few entries. Like I said, it only started doing this in the last hour. It was fine this morning. You people always say report it, but nothing ever comes out of it.
